14
00:01:33,490 --> 00:01:37,480
=My Calorie Boy=

15
00:01:38,020 --> 00:01:40,940
=Episode 19=
(My Summer Holiday, My Say)

16
00:01:41,450 --> 00:01:42,170
You've studied Taekwondo

17
00:01:42,330 --> 00:01:43,170
for so many years.

18
00:01:43,330 --> 00:01:44,450
You're guaranteed to excel
if you choose a sports major.

19
00:01:44,660 --> 00:01:45,890
Why do you have to choose arts?

20
00:01:46,220 --> 00:01:47,090
After you graduate,

21
00:01:47,220 --> 00:01:48,610
I'll fund you

22
00:01:48,780 --> 00:01:49,700
to open up a Taekwondo academy.

23
00:01:49,890 --> 00:01:50,970
Or if you think that's too much work,

24
00:01:51,140 --> 00:01:51,810
then we can start

25
00:01:51,970 --> 00:01:53,170
a wedding planning company
and make money together.

26
00:01:53,330 --> 00:01:54,220
Doesn't that sound nice?

27
00:01:54,530 --> 00:01:56,450
I don't want to start
a wedding planning company!

28
00:01:56,610 --> 00:01:57,940
I want to study interior design!

29
00:01:58,300 --> 00:01:59,220
How are you any different

30
00:01:59,330 --> 00:01:59,970
from Xu Jingjing's mother

31
00:02:00,140 --> 00:02:01,020
if you plan my life out for me?

32
00:02:01,250 --> 00:02:02,220
What do you mean...

33
00:02:03,250 --> 00:02:04,250
I...

34
00:02:08,210 --> 00:02:08,860
Jingjing!

35
00:02:12,860 --> 00:02:13,980
Look at your daughter!

36
00:02:14,380 --> 00:02:15,450
She slammed the door on me!

37
00:02:21,730 --> 00:02:22,770
My daughter has changed.

38
00:02:23,210 --> 00:02:23,820
Yes.

39
00:02:24,260 --> 00:02:25,770
She dares to talk back to us now.

40
00:02:26,300 --> 00:02:26,980
No.

41
00:02:27,770 --> 00:02:28,420
She has become

42
00:02:28,580 --> 00:02:29,930
more assertive

43
00:02:30,210 --> 00:02:31,140
and knows what she wants now.

44
00:02:32,490 --> 00:02:33,140
Look at how much she has changed

45
00:02:33,300 --> 00:02:34,140
in the past year.

46
00:02:34,380 --> 00:02:35,020
Her grades went up

47
00:02:35,210 --> 00:02:36,260
so much.

48
00:02:36,700 --> 00:02:37,450
And look what she did

49
00:02:37,860 --> 00:02:38,490
today.

50
00:02:38,730 --> 00:02:40,100
(Revision Schedule)
She must've put a lot of work

51
00:02:40,260 --> 00:02:41,210
(Revision Schedule)
and effort into this.

52
00:02:41,420 --> 00:02:42,210
She did all of this

53
00:02:42,420 --> 00:02:43,100
just

54
00:02:43,260 --> 00:02:44,020
to convince us.

55
00:02:44,730 --> 00:02:45,890
Xu, I'm serious.

56
00:02:46,300 --> 00:02:46,820
I think

57
00:02:47,020 --> 00:02:47,770
we can't let our daughter

58
00:02:47,930 --> 00:02:48,890
down.

59
00:02:49,300 --> 00:02:50,580
Just let her try.

60
00:02:50,930 --> 00:02:51,730
If she does fail,

61
00:02:51,890 --> 00:02:52,770
she'll give up.

62
00:02:52,980 --> 00:02:53,490
If she actually fails,

63
00:02:53,700 --> 00:02:55,730
it'll be even harder for her!

64
00:02:55,890 --> 00:02:56,490
Why are you so sure

65
00:02:56,650 --> 00:02:57,730
that she would fail?

66
00:02:58,020 --> 00:02:59,300
I'm not underestimating our daughter.

67
00:02:59,490 --> 00:03:00,100
But do you know

68
00:03:00,260 --> 00:03:01,380
how many people who take
the unified examination

69
00:03:01,540 --> 00:03:02,700
for art students actually end up
getting admitted?

70
00:03:03,610 --> 00:03:05,020
It's even more competitive
than the college entrance examination.

71
00:03:05,170 --> 00:03:06,490
There aren't enough opportunities

72
00:03:06,650 --> 00:03:08,580
to go around, Jiaren.

73
00:03:09,330 --> 00:03:10,100
Jingjing

74
00:03:10,300 --> 00:03:11,700
has always been competitive
and prideful.

75
00:03:12,050 --> 00:03:12,860
If she gives her all

76
00:03:13,020 --> 00:03:14,330
into this

77
00:03:14,490 --> 00:03:16,100
and fails,

78
00:03:16,300 --> 00:03:18,100
she might never get up again.

79
00:03:18,300 --> 00:03:19,050
How will she

80
00:03:19,260 --> 00:03:21,020
get up and take
the college entrance exam then?

81
00:03:21,930 --> 00:03:23,100
It'll be too late.

82
00:03:29,820 --> 00:03:30,490
I'm sorry,

83
00:03:31,020 --> 00:03:31,860
little piggy.

84
00:03:40,580 --> 00:03:41,170
100...

85
00:03:41,860 --> 00:03:42,380
200...

86
00:03:52,600 --> 00:03:54,560
(Balance, 638.22)

87
00:03:58,260 --> 00:04:00,450
I'm one digit short...

88
00:04:15,240 --> 00:04:19,200
(ArtDragon Martial Arte Taekwondo)

89
00:04:21,880 --> 00:04:22,740
(Taekwondo)

90
00:04:22,740 --> 00:04:23,700
Ow...

91
00:04:24,060 --> 00:04:25,530
Instructor, please...
I can't take it anymore...

92
00:04:25,650 --> 00:04:26,380
Hang in there.

93
00:04:31,260 --> 00:04:32,090
Instructor Fan.

94
00:04:34,970 --> 00:04:35,890
Jingjing, you're here.

95
00:04:36,620 --> 00:04:37,290
I haven't seen you in a while.

96
00:04:37,650 --> 00:04:38,700
Well, I had some free time on my hands,

97
00:04:38,890 --> 00:04:39,820
so I thought I would drop by.

98
00:04:40,940 --> 00:04:42,450
All right. Take a break.

99
00:04:44,380 --> 00:04:45,090
I'm sorry

100
00:04:45,380 --> 00:04:46,650
I haven't stopped by in a while.

101
00:04:46,850 --> 00:04:47,650
I know you're busy.

102
00:04:48,410 --> 00:04:49,090
You'll be taking

103
00:04:49,260 --> 00:04:50,260
the college entrance examination
next year, right?

104
00:04:51,260 --> 00:04:53,290
But I've been practising every day.

105
00:04:53,940 --> 00:04:55,890
I saw on your Wechat Moments

106
00:04:56,700 --> 00:04:57,580
that you're hiring instructors.

107
00:04:57,740 --> 00:04:58,330
Yes.

108
00:04:59,060 --> 00:04:59,770
But you just missed it.

109
00:04:59,970 --> 00:05:01,500
A boy came by earlier.

110
00:05:01,940 --> 00:05:03,210
He fit the criteria,

111
00:05:03,380 --> 00:05:04,410
so I gave him the job.

112
00:05:04,530 --> 00:05:05,940
I'll be leaving now, Instructor Fan.

113
00:05:08,180 --> 00:05:09,060
Xu Jingjing?

114
00:05:10,450 --> 00:05:11,290
Gao Zhan?

115
00:05:14,500 --> 00:05:15,770
You guys know each other?

116
00:05:16,650 --> 00:05:17,740
We're classmates.

117
00:05:18,770 --> 00:05:19,290
Well,

118
00:05:19,500 --> 00:05:20,820
your class is certainly filled
with talents.

119
00:05:22,410 --> 00:05:23,410
Well,

120
00:05:23,530 --> 00:05:24,140
since you filled the position,

121
00:05:24,290 --> 00:05:25,090
I'll take my leave then, Instructor Fan.

122
00:05:25,770 --> 00:05:26,410
Since you're here,

123
00:05:26,700 --> 00:05:27,210
do you want to join us

124
00:05:27,210 --> 00:05:27,650
for practice?

125
00:05:28,060 --> 00:05:28,450
No, that's all right.

126
00:05:28,620 --> 00:05:29,770
I just remembered
that I had something to do.

127
00:05:30,580 --> 00:05:31,330
I'll be leaving now.

128
00:05:35,410 --> 00:05:36,700
All right. Gather around.

129
00:05:37,820 --> 00:05:38,580
Hurry up.

130
00:05:41,820 --> 00:05:42,450
Xu Jingjing!

131
00:05:44,970 --> 00:05:45,820
Are you looking for a part-time job

132
00:05:45,970 --> 00:05:46,620
during the summer break too?

133
00:05:49,890 --> 00:05:51,380
I discussed it with Instructor Fan.

134
00:05:52,650 --> 00:05:53,820
I don't have much experience.

135
00:05:54,060 --> 00:05:55,450
We can teach the classes together.

136
00:05:55,740 --> 00:05:56,890
We'll split the money.

137
00:05:57,890 --> 00:05:59,020
I... I don't think that's appropriate...

138
00:05:59,180 --> 00:06:00,500
You don't have to be courteous.

139
00:06:02,260 --> 00:06:03,450
Thanks a lot, then, Gao Zhan.

140
00:06:03,700 --> 00:06:04,700
You really helped me out.

141
00:06:05,060 --> 00:06:06,890
But why do you need a part-time job?

142
00:06:07,740 --> 00:06:08,380
Well,

143
00:06:08,530 --> 00:06:09,580
I want to apply for a design course.

144
00:06:09,740 --> 00:06:10,180
But to do that,

145
00:06:10,330 --> 00:06:11,410
I'll have to pass
the unified exam for art students first.

146
00:06:11,620 --> 00:06:12,700
So I'm planning on enrolling

147
00:06:12,850 --> 00:06:14,090
in an art class during the summer.

148
00:06:14,450 --> 00:06:15,620
Didn't your parents agree?

149
00:06:18,380 --> 00:06:18,890
What about you?

150
00:06:19,650 --> 00:06:20,650
Why do you need a job?

151
00:06:21,940 --> 00:06:23,290
I'm in a similar situation.

152
00:06:24,700 --> 00:06:25,820
I want to save up money

153
00:06:26,060 --> 00:06:27,260
to do myopia surgery.

154
00:06:28,180 --> 00:06:29,530
But why would you need

155
00:06:29,700 --> 00:06:30,740
to pay for that yourself?

156
00:06:32,850 --> 00:06:33,850
If I tell you the truth,

157
00:06:34,060 --> 00:06:35,260
would you keep it a secret?

158
00:06:36,890 --> 00:06:38,330
I wanted to go to Beijing

159
00:06:38,890 --> 00:06:40,210
to apply
to the Public Security University.

160
00:06:41,410 --> 00:06:42,330
You want to be a police officer

161
00:06:42,580 --> 00:06:43,450
like your dad.

162
00:06:44,740 --> 00:06:45,140
But my mom

163
00:06:45,330 --> 00:06:46,330
would never say yes.

164
00:06:46,890 --> 00:06:48,180
My dad died in the line of duty.

165
00:06:49,330 --> 00:06:50,850
She would freak out.

166
00:06:52,330 --> 00:06:53,260
So

167
00:06:53,580 --> 00:06:54,650
you want to earn money
for the surgery yourself.

168
00:06:56,140 --> 00:06:57,180
Just like how you want to earn money

169
00:06:57,380 --> 00:06:58,210
for your tuition fee.

170
00:06:59,140 --> 00:06:59,620
Oh, right.

171
00:07:00,090 --> 00:07:01,500
If you split the money with me,

172
00:07:01,650 --> 00:07:02,140
will you have enough

173
00:07:02,290 --> 00:07:03,330
for the surgery?

174
00:07:03,890 --> 00:07:05,060
Instructor Fan said

175
00:07:05,290 --> 00:07:06,180
that if we do well,

176
00:07:06,330 --> 00:07:06,940
he might open

177
00:07:07,140 --> 00:07:07,850
another children's class

178
00:07:08,060 --> 00:07:08,650
in the summer.

179
00:07:09,060 --> 00:07:10,330
That'll make up
for the rest of the money.

180
00:07:12,650 --> 00:07:13,210
Gao Zhan,

181
00:07:14,450 --> 00:07:15,210
thank you.

182
00:07:17,500 --> 00:07:18,210
I look forward to working with you.

183
00:07:20,260 --> 00:07:20,940
Miss Zhou,

184
00:07:21,850 --> 00:07:22,580
I have something

185
00:07:22,890 --> 00:07:23,970
to discuss with you.

186
00:07:24,650 --> 00:07:25,410
Go ahead.

187
00:07:29,090 --> 00:07:31,620
It's about the tuition fee...

188
00:07:32,060 --> 00:07:33,580
I'm afraid we can't go any lower.

189
00:07:33,890 --> 00:07:34,650
All the other kids

190
00:07:34,820 --> 00:07:35,620
pay the same amount.

191
00:07:35,890 --> 00:07:36,620
No.

192
00:07:36,940 --> 00:07:38,060
I meant to ask

193
00:07:38,330 --> 00:07:40,060
if I could be billed by the day.

194
00:07:40,580 --> 00:07:41,650
Billed by the day?

195
00:07:42,210 --> 00:07:43,620
Do you have a problem?

196
00:07:44,380 --> 00:07:45,290
Um...

197
00:07:45,700 --> 00:07:46,770
My family...

198
00:07:46,940 --> 00:07:47,500
Miss Zhou,

199
00:07:47,970 --> 00:07:49,820
Jingjing's family
isn't exactly well-off.

200
00:07:51,260 --> 00:07:51,850
Right.

201
00:07:52,620 --> 00:07:53,770
My family isn't well-off.

202
00:07:54,060 --> 00:07:54,620
So could you please

203
00:07:54,820 --> 00:07:55,850
make an exception?

204
00:07:56,140 --> 00:07:57,820
But we've always required students

205
00:07:57,970 --> 00:07:59,450
to settle the fees in one lump sum.

206
00:07:59,890 --> 00:08:01,580
Miss Zhou, help Jingjing out.

207
00:08:01,740 --> 00:08:03,210
She really likes art.

208
00:08:06,210 --> 00:08:06,940
How about this?

209
00:08:07,380 --> 00:08:08,380
I'll put your name down.

210
00:08:08,850 --> 00:08:10,530
For the first five days,
you can pay by the day.

211
00:08:11,180 --> 00:08:12,090
You can use the five days

212
00:08:12,290 --> 00:08:13,940
to see if art is for you.

213
00:08:14,090 --> 00:08:15,410
If you decide to continue,

214
00:08:15,740 --> 00:08:16,890
you'll have to settle the rest
of the fees in one go.

215
00:08:17,060 --> 00:08:17,500
Okay!

216
00:08:17,650 --> 00:08:18,380
Thank you, Miss Zhou.

217
00:08:27,850 --> 00:08:29,020
You're going to teach Taekwondo?

218
00:08:31,260 --> 00:08:32,530
My friend and I talked about this.

219
00:08:32,810 --> 00:08:34,020
We'll teach the classes together.

220
00:08:34,170 --> 00:08:35,050
I'll start this weekend.

221
00:08:38,020 --> 00:08:39,140
I don't mean anything else by that.

222
00:08:39,380 --> 00:08:40,380
I just want to let you guys know

223
00:08:40,530 --> 00:08:41,260
that I can

224
00:08:41,620 --> 00:08:42,620
pay the fees myself.

225
00:08:52,890 --> 00:08:53,980
Don't mind him, Jingjing.

226
00:08:54,140 --> 00:08:55,290
Eat.

227
00:08:56,930 --> 00:08:58,890
The money you earn
from teaching Taekwondo

228
00:08:59,810 --> 00:09:00,930
won't be enough to cover
the tuition fees, right?

229
00:09:01,220 --> 00:09:01,890
It's fine, Mom.

230
00:09:02,140 --> 00:09:02,860
Don't worry.

231
00:09:03,140 --> 00:09:04,100
I can handle this myself.

232
00:09:04,650 --> 00:09:05,650
I just want to show him

233
00:09:05,810 --> 00:09:06,650
my resolve.

234
00:09:07,740 --> 00:09:08,530
Let's eat.

235
00:09:15,650 --> 00:09:17,620
You've gained weight
because of your injury.

236
00:09:17,930 --> 00:09:19,220
You need to control your diet.

237
00:09:24,860 --> 00:09:25,410
Oh, right.

238
00:09:26,570 --> 00:09:27,050
I found you

239
00:09:27,260 --> 00:09:28,650
a teacher
from the advanced class, Miss Zhao.

240
00:09:29,220 --> 00:09:30,380
They say

241
00:09:30,930 --> 00:09:32,140
that a lot of her students

242
00:09:32,340 --> 00:09:33,810
made it into dance academies.

243
00:09:34,380 --> 00:09:34,890
You'll train under her

244
00:09:35,050 --> 00:09:35,930
for the summer.

245
00:09:36,620 --> 00:09:37,690
She just recovered.

246
00:09:37,890 --> 00:09:39,140
Can't you give her
a bit more time to rest?

247
00:09:39,530 --> 00:09:40,740
We don't have time to lose.

248
00:09:41,380 --> 00:09:42,380
It's because of her injury

249
00:09:42,810 --> 00:09:43,810
that she is still in place

250
00:09:44,140 --> 00:09:45,570
when others have already gotten ahead.

251
00:09:47,050 --> 00:09:47,690
If you ask me,

252
00:09:47,890 --> 00:09:50,020
you should drop

253
00:09:50,380 --> 00:09:51,530
that thesis writing class too.

254
00:09:52,260 --> 00:09:53,380
It would be better for you
to use that time

255
00:09:53,500 --> 00:09:54,770
to practise your dance moves.

256
00:09:56,260 --> 00:09:57,100
What if

257
00:09:57,980 --> 00:09:59,290
I failed the college entrance exam
for art students?

258
00:10:00,020 --> 00:10:01,020
So be it.

259
00:10:01,340 --> 00:10:01,860
It's fine.

260
00:10:02,260 --> 00:10:03,290
You can try again next year.

261
00:10:04,290 --> 00:10:05,530
What are you saying?

262
00:10:05,690 --> 00:10:07,530
Is that any way to teach your child?

263
00:10:08,650 --> 00:10:09,220
And you.

264
00:10:09,500 --> 00:10:10,930
Already thinking about failing
before even taking the exam.

265
00:10:11,290 --> 00:10:12,530
How are you supposed to do well
with an attitude like that?

266
00:10:17,740 --> 00:10:18,410
Mom,

267
00:10:21,050 --> 00:10:22,980
do I have to get into the dance academy?

268
00:10:32,100 --> 00:10:32,740
Xu Jingjing,

269
00:10:34,100 --> 00:10:35,740
do you know how much energy and money

270
00:10:36,290 --> 00:10:37,170
I have invested

271
00:10:37,340 --> 00:10:38,050
in raising you

272
00:10:38,650 --> 00:10:39,620
to dance ballet

273
00:10:39,770 --> 00:10:40,620
since you were a child?

274
00:10:41,980 --> 00:10:43,170
Do you know how much effort it took

275
00:10:43,340 --> 00:10:45,140
to get Miss Zhao to accept you?

276
00:10:46,050 --> 00:10:47,050
Normally, she only accepts students

277
00:10:47,170 --> 00:10:48,860
from schools affiliated
with dance academies.

278
00:10:49,170 --> 00:10:50,340
She would've never been

279
00:10:50,570 --> 00:10:51,020
spared a glance

280
00:10:51,220 --> 00:10:52,340
at someone like you
from an ordinary high school.

281
00:10:53,410 --> 00:10:54,380
Hearing you say that

282
00:10:54,740 --> 00:10:56,100
really makes me disappointed.

283
00:10:57,770 --> 00:10:58,930
All right. I understand, Mom.

284
00:10:59,530 --> 00:11:00,650
I will go.

285
00:11:12,640 --> 00:11:15,560
(Application Form
