what's going on between you two...

598
00:24:33,130 --> 00:24:34,460
Why?

599
00:24:34,740 --> 00:24:35,810
Why would she want

600
00:24:36,130 --> 00:24:37,530
to break up with me all of a sudden?

601
00:24:37,530 --> 00:24:38,330
You...

602
00:24:39,610 --> 00:24:40,660
You didn't do anything wrong

603
