609
00:24:47,260 --> 00:24:48,020
Not really.

610
00:24:48,810 --> 00:24:49,370
Gao Zhan,

611
00:24:49,850 --> 00:24:50,700
we formed an alliance

612
00:24:50,940 --> 00:24:52,290
that day, didn't we?

613
00:24:53,130 --> 00:24:54,850
Well, I wouldn't call it an alliance.

614
00:24:55,420 --> 00:24:56,740
All right, all right. Fine.

615
00:24:56,940 --> 00:24:57,940
I came to you

616
00:24:58,130 --> 00:24:58,770
to see

617
00:24:59,260 --> 00:25:00,700
if you could go back

618
00:25:01,500 --> 00:25:03,330
and help me ask your mom

619
00:25:04,130 --> 00:25:05,700
why did she say those things today.

620
00:25:11,610 --> 00:25:12,290
All right.

621
00:25:13,460 --> 00:25:14,900
I know that's too much to ask of you.

622
00:25:15,810 --> 00:25:16,660
You get busy then.

623
00:25:17,420 --> 00:25:18,460
I'll take my leave now.

624
00:25:20,420 --> 00:25:21,940
Oh, why...

625
00:25:29,900 --> 00:25:32,050
Oh, that Gao Zhan!

626
00:25:32,980 --> 00:25:34,020
How could he side

627
00:25:34,180 --> 00:25:35,130
with Snape?

628
00:25:36,130 --> 00:25:37,050
I just don't understand him.

629
00:25:42,200 --> 00:25:43,240
(Xu Jingjing)

630
00:25:53,660 --> 00:25:54,770
Why are you calling me?

631
00:25:55,980 --> 00:25:57,900
I was bored on my way home.

632
00:25:58,900 --> 00:26:00,530
Isn't Gao Zhan with you?

633
00:26:01,420 --> 00:26:02,420
I was just about to tell you about him.

634
00:26:02,610 --> 00:26:03,180
Listen.

635
00:26:03,330 --> 00:26:05,050
He was "amazing" today!

636
00:26:07,850 --> 00:26:08,500
Do you know why?

637
00:26:08,610 --> 00:26:09,180
It's Xu Jingjing.

638
00:26:09,370 --> 00:26:10,180
What do I want for dinner?

639
00:26:10,370 --> 00:26:11,020
You decide.

640
00:26:11,260 --> 00:26:12,290
I'm happy to have anything with you.

641
00:26:15,130 --> 00:26:16,180
Hello? Sorry.

642
00:26:17,330 --> 00:26:18,020
That was Xu Jingjing.

643
00:26:18,330 --> 00:26:19,500
She asked me
what we were getting for dinner.

644
00:26:19,770 --> 00:26:20,460
Carry on.

645
00:26:20,770 --> 00:26:21,460
What about Gao Zhan?

646
00:26:21,660 --> 00:26:22,370
What did he do?

647
00:26:22,700 --> 00:26:23,290
Oh, nothing.

648
00:26:23,530 --> 00:26:24,900
I just wanted to tell you

649
00:26:25,220 --> 00:26:26,090
that he looked so cool

650
00:26:26,460 --> 00:26:27,980
in the Taekwondo uniform today.

651
00:26:28,130 --> 00:26:29,290
Go and get dinner with Xu Jingjing.

652
00:26:29,460 --> 00:26:30,500
Gao Zhan and I
are going out for dinner together too.

653
00:26:30,700 --> 00:26:31,460
Okay. See you.

654
