(Publish)

658
00:26:54,160 --> 00:26:56,540
(Kang Jiawei. I didn't expect you
to be such a foodie.)

659
00:27:05,900 --> 00:27:06,500
You can have this.

660
00:27:09,570 --> 00:27:11,020
(You eat quite a lot.)

661
00:27:15,220 --> 00:27:15,770
Waiter!

662
00:27:16,260 --> 00:27:17,290
Three more servings of steamed buns!

663
00:27:17,520 --> 00:27:18,720
(Xu Jingjing. I didn't know you like
Beef and Onion Buns too.)

664
00:27:18,810 --> 00:27:19,610
