665
00:27:19,610 --> 00:27:20,700
(beef and scallion buns too.)

666
00:27:21,020 --> 00:27:21,610
(Happy!)

667
00:27:27,080 --> 00:27:28,040
(Imported snacks. Souvenirs. Fruits.)

