00:27:41,500 --> 00:27:45,020
(An evening filled
with the fragrance of peaches.)

669
00:27:49,940 --> 00:27:51,290
I'll carry it.

670
00:27:57,740 --> 00:27:58,740
Little girl,

671
00:27:59,290 --> 00:28:00,610
why are you

672
00:28:00,810 --> 00:28:01,900
following us?

673
00:28:02,920 --> 00:28:05,240
(While taking a walk after dinner,
we ran into a granny...)

674
00:28:10,130 --> 00:28:10,940
(While taking a walk after dinner,)

675
00:28:11,130 --> 00:28:11,530
(we)

676
00:28:11,530 --> 00:28:13,460
(ran into a granny
who insisted that we buy her flowers.)

677
00:28:26,020 --> 00:28:27,770
(Which KTV has the best sound system?)

678
00:28:31,530 --> 00:28:33,260
(I haven't gone clubbing for long.)

679
00:28:40,460 --> 00:28:41,810
What the heck...

680
00:28:42,330 --> 00:28:43,660
What am I doing?

681
00:28:46,220 --> 00:28:47,570
Not going to bed yet, Mom?

682
00:28:48,090 --> 00:28:49,260
No. I'll go to sleep in a bit.

683
00:28:49,980 --> 00:28:50,850
Why aren't you in bed yet?

684
00:28:52,530 --> 00:28:53,570
I came out to get some water.

685
00:29:03,700 --> 00:29:04,420
Is something wrong?

686
00:29:07,810 --> 00:29:08,420
Mom,

687
00:29:09,500 --> 00:29:11,460
what's going on between you and Mr. Ni?

688
00:29:12,610 --> 00:29:13,370
Nothing.

689
00:29:14,180 --> 00:29:14,570
Kids shouldn't interfere

690
00:29:14,770 --> 00:29:15,740
with adult matters.

691
00:29:18,130 --> 00:29:19,050
Didn't you say

692
00:29:19,220 --> 00:29:20,500
you were happy with him?

693
00:29:21,130 --> 00:29:22,220
So why are you breaking up with him now?

694
00:29:23,810 --> 00:29:25,220
Aren't you happy

695
00:29:25,570 --> 00:29:26,420
to hear that we're breaking up?

696
00:29:27,330 --> 00:29:27,900
Mom,

697
00:29:28,130 --> 00:29:29,660
you can't pin that on me.

698
00:29:30,460 --> 00:29:31,700
I have no objections whatsoever

699
00:29:31,900 --> 00:29:33,050
to your relationship with him now.

700
00:29:34,220 --> 00:29:35,050
I actually think

701
00:29:35,290 --> 00:29:36,770
that Mr. Ni

702
00:29:37,420 --> 00:29:38,530
is a pretty decent guy.

703
00:29:43,940 --> 00:29:44,740
You really want to know?

704
00:29:56,370 --> 00:29:57,500
You'll be heading into Grade 12 soon.

705
00:29:58,220 --> 00:30:00,130
It's the most crucial year for you.

706
00:30:00,850 --> 00:30:02,330
I was too selfish before this.

707
00:30:03,220 --> 00:30:04,420
So I don't want to do anything

708
00:30:04,610 --> 00:30:05,260
that might

709
00:30:05,460 --> 00:30:06,850
affect your taking
your college entrance exam now.

710
00:30:07,940 --> 00:30:09,130
Why would your being with Mr. Ni

711
00:30:09,330 --> 00:30:10,370
affect me?

712
00:30:11,850 --> 00:30:13,850
If I accept Mr. Ni

713
00:30:14,050 --> 00:30:14,980
and we decide to come together

714
00:30:15,700 --> 00:30:17,370
and reconstitute a family,

715
00:30:18,290 --> 00:30:19,420
will you be okay with that?

716
00:30:20,180 --> 00:30:20,850
Yes.

717
00:30:21,130 --> 00:30:22,810
I've tolerated Dapeng for two years.

718
00:30:25,460 --> 00:30:26,700
Reconstituting a family

719
00:30:26,900 --> 00:30:28,570
isn't as easy or simple as you think.

720
00:30:29,290 --> 00:30:31,050
We'll need to work
on all aspects of our lives.

721
00:30:31,850 --> 00:30:32,940
What if we live together

722
00:30:33,130 --> 00:30:33,940
in the same space

723
00:30:34,770 --> 00:30:35,660
and find out
that we aren't compatible?

724
00:30:36,460 --> 00:30:37,660
We can't waste all our time

725
00:30:37,900 --> 00:30:38,290
on solving

726
00:30:38,500 --> 00:30:39,660
family conflicts.

727
00:30:39,900 --> 00:30:40,460
Mom,

728
00:30:40,700 --> 00:30:41,570
let's leave that out for now.

729
00:30:41,810 --> 00:30:43,130
Set aside everything

730
00:30:43,500 --> 00:30:44,330
and just tell me

731
00:30:44,700 --> 00:30:46,700
if you still have feelings for Mr. Ni.

732
00:30:53,700 --> 00:30:54,420
All right.

733
00:30:55,420 --> 00:30:56,500
It's late.

734
00:30:56,740 --> 00:30:57,220
Get some rest.

735
00:30:57,420 --> 00:30:58,500
You need to get up early tomorrow.

736
00:30:59,530 --> 00:31:00,130
But...

737
00:31:00,370 --> 00:31:01,130
No buts.

738
00:31:02,090 --> 00:31:03,290
I know what you mean.

739
00:31:05,020 --> 00:31:05,980
I'll give it more thought.

740
00:32:00,260 --> 00:32:00,770
Next,

741
00:32:00,980 --> 00:32:01,850
let's take a look at the eighth step.

742
00:32:02,050 --> 00:32:02,530
For the eighth step,

743
00:32:02,770 --> 00:32:03,810
we will have

744
00:32:03,980 --> 00:32:04,530
to examine,

745
00:32:04,740 --> 00:32:06,460
standardise, and edit the paper

746
00:32:06,700 --> 00:32:07,530
in a technical manner.

747
00:32:07,770 --> 00:32:08,290
Next,

748
00:32:08,500 --> 00:32:09,420
choose the topic of your thesis.

749
00:32:09,660 --> 00:32:11,050
There are two points to consider
when choosing your topic.

750
00:32:11,260 --> 00:32:12,500
The size

751
00:32:12,740 --> 00:32:14,330
and the value of the topic.

752
00:32:14,610 --> 00:32:15,810
How do we gauge the size of a topic?

753
00:32:16,020 --> 00:32:17,290
First, we look at the scope.

754
00:32:17,330 --> 00:32:18,770
(Kang Jiawei. Which KTV has a better sound system?)
When choosing a topic

755
00:32:19,050 --> 00:32:19,980
(While taking a walk after dinner, we ran into a granny...)
for your thesis,

756
00:32:20,180 --> 00:32:21,660
you need to consider

757
00:32:21,940 --> 00:32:23,460
the breadth of the content
and the scope of the topic.

758
00:32:24,050 --> 00:32:25,370
(Only 3 days of Moments are viewable.)
You must consider your own writing abilities

759
00:32:25,570 --> 00:32:27,020
(Only 3 days of Moments are viewable.)
when choosing your topic.

760
00:32:27,290 --> 00:32:28,460
If the scope is too wide,

761
00:32:28,660 --> 00:32:29,370
it'll be difficult for you
to grasp the focus.

762
00:32:29,570 --> 00:32:30,610
Pay attention.

763
00:32:30,940 --> 00:32:32,050
Don't be scrolling on your phone.

764
00:32:39,260 --> 00:32:39,740
Good morning.

765
00:32:40,810 --> 00:32:41,330
You're here.

766
00:32:42,290 --> 00:32:43,260
I left without saying goodbye

767
00:32:43,420 --> 00:32:44,090
after class yesterday.

768
00:32:44,290 --> 00:32:45,050
Sorry.

769
00:32:45,660 --> 00:32:46,370
It's fine.

770
00:32:47,660 --> 00:32:49,020
Dapeng's dad came to see me.

771
00:32:49,660 --> 00:32:51,810
He told me that my mom
wanted to break up with him.

772
00:32:52,660 --> 00:32:54,050
Break up?

773
00:32:54,330 --> 00:32:55,090
Why?

774
00:32:55,460 --> 00:32:56,810
Did you talk to your mom about it?

775
00:32:57,290 --> 00:32:57,810
I did.

776
00:32:58,700 --> 00:32:59,850
From what she said, it sounds like
her main concern is not wanting

777
00:33:00,980 --> 00:33:02,330
their relationship to affect my
taking the college entrance exam.

778
00:33:02,700 --> 00:33:03,500
That's all?

779
00:33:10,180 --> 00:33:11,220
I couldn't understand her either.

780
00:33:11,810 --> 00:33:12,900
It feels like I wouldn't be doing

781
00:33:13,090 --> 00:33:14,050
right by her sacrifice if I don't try

782
00:33:14,290 --> 00:33:15,740
to make it into Tsinghua University
or Beijing University.

783
00:33:17,810 --> 00:33:19,370
What are you going to do then?

784
00:33:20,330 --> 00:33:21,570
I've said what I should.

785
00:33:23,130 --> 00:33:24,180
But that's not fair

786
00:33:24,420 --> 00:33:25,660
to Mr. Ni.

787
00:33:28,570 --> 00:33:30,260
If I do get accepted
into Public Security University,

788
00:33:30,980 --> 00:33:32,570
I'll be studying in Beijing
for four years.

789
00:33:34,090 --> 00:33:34,740
In fact,

790
00:33:35,370 --> 00:33:36,370
I would like it if there was someone

791
00:33:36,570 --> 00:33:37,180
to take care of her

792
00:33:37,370 --> 00:33:38,290
while I'm away.

793
00:33:40,370 --> 00:33:40,940
Is that

794
00:33:41,130 --> 00:33:42,220
too selfish of me?

795
00:33:43,020 --> 00:33:44,130
Not at all.

796
00:33:44,500 --> 00:33:45,130
You're her son.

797
00:33:45,330 --> 00:33:46,660
It's normal for you to think that way.

798
00:33:47,090 --> 00:33:47,810
Really?

799
00:33:48,370 --> 00:33:49,090
I think

800
00:33:49,330 --> 00:33:50,130
you should support

801
00:33:50,330 --> 00:33:50,810
Mr. Ni

802
00:33:51,020 --> 00:33:52,220
right now

803
00:33:52,420 --> 00:33:54,370
and convince your mom
to get back together with him.

804
00:34:02,530 --> 00:34:03,770
Will you help me?

805
00:34:08,730 --> 00:34:09,250
Mr. Ni,

806
00:34:09,860 --> 00:34:10,730
I've told you

807
00:34:10,940 --> 00:34:12,460
the general situation in the message.

808
00:34:13,650 --> 00:34:14,250
Yes.

809
00:34:15,420 --> 00:34:16,090
But

810
00:34:17,050 --> 00:34:17,940
I think your mom

811
00:34:18,130 --> 00:34:19,020
made a fair point.

812
00:34:20,020 --> 00:34:20,610
I mean,

813
00:34:20,860 --> 00:34:22,090
you're different from Pengpeng.

814
00:34:22,300 --> 00:34:22,780
You're aiming

815
00:34:22,980 --> 00:34:23,820
for Tsinghua University
and Beijing University.

816
00:34:24,020 --> 00:34:24,570
No, you...

817
00:34:24,980 --> 00:34:25,570
You guys can say whatever you want,

818
00:34:25,780 --> 00:34:26,690
but why drag me into this?

819
00:34:27,050 --> 00:34:27,610
No, you...

820
00:34:27,820 --> 00:34:28,420
Mr. Ni.

821
00:34:29,210 --> 00:34:30,020
Gao Zhan is talking to you.

822
00:34:30,820 --> 00:34:31,500
Go on.

823
00:34:31,730 --> 00:34:32,500
I still think

824
00:34:33,340 --> 00:34:34,380
you should have a proper talk

825
00:34:34,570 --> 00:34:35,380
about this with my mom.

826
00:34:36,780 --> 00:34:38,090
You shouldn't break up
over something like this.

827
00:34:38,820 --> 00:34:39,530
I would not let my studies

828
00:34:39,730 --> 00:34:40,130
be affected

829
00:34:40,340 --> 00:34:41,130
by your relationship.

830
00:34:42,380 --> 00:34:43,130
Gao Zhan,

831
00:34:44,690 --> 00:34:45,940
is that what you truly think?

832
00:34:47,300 --> 00:34:48,380
I'm responsible for my own studies.

833
00:34:48,730 --> 00:34:49,860
It has nothing to do

834
00:34:49,860 --> 00:34:50,420
with whether you're together.

835
00:34:50,610 --> 00:34:51,340
Then...

836
00:34:51,780 --> 00:34:53,210
The proposal...

837
00:34:53,570 --> 00:34:55,130
I think what matters the most

838
00:34:55,420 --> 00:34:56,210
is your sincerity.

839
00:34:57,460 --> 00:34:58,250
First,

840
00:34:58,860 --> 00:34:59,690
you need

841
00:34:59,900 --> 00:35:01,050
to propose to my mom properly.

842
00:35:01,460 --> 00:35:02,730
Like what they do in dramas.

843
00:35:03,130 --> 00:35:04,020
Make a heart

844
00:35:04,460 --> 00:35:05,570
with candles below my house

845
00:35:05,940 --> 00:35:07,500
and fill the middle with roses.

846
00:35:07,650 --> 00:35:08,780
Do you play the guitar?

847
00:35:09,420 --> 00:35:10,730
If you do,

848
00:35:10,940 --> 00:35:11,940
