849
00:35:12,130 --> 00:35:13,130
Wait. Stop.

850
00:35:14,500 --> 00:35:15,730
I can't listen to any more of this.

851
00:35:16,250 --> 00:35:17,900
What cliche is that?

852
00:35:18,090 --> 00:35:19,170
That's way too corny.

853
00:35:20,300 --> 00:35:20,860
Is it?

854
00:35:22,090 --> 00:35:22,860
Is it not?

855
00:35:23,980 --> 00:35:25,940
I thought it was romantic.

856
00:35:27,050 --> 00:35:27,900
A guy like you
who knows nothing

857
00:35:28,090 --> 00:35:29,340
about what girls want
deserves to be single for life.

858
00:35:29,860 --> 00:35:30,380
Well, Xu Jingjing,

