00:35:30,650 --> 00:35:32,130
tells us what sort of proposals

860
00:35:32,380 --> 00:35:33,300
girls would like then.

861
00:35:33,900 --> 00:35:34,530
First of all,

862
00:35:35,090 --> 00:35:36,900
we need to analyse the target.

863
00:35:37,500 --> 00:35:38,090
What does Madam Shi work as?

864
00:35:38,460 --> 00:35:39,460
She's the Editor-in-Chief of a magazine.

865
00:35:39,690 --> 00:35:40,380
She is cultured.

866
00:35:40,820 --> 00:35:41,650
So she would want something

867
00:35:41,900 --> 00:35:42,610
sophisticated and simple.

868
00:35:42,820 --> 00:35:43,380
She would hate

869
00:35:43,570 --> 00:35:44,300
something that's too garish.

870
00:35:46,210 --> 00:35:47,020
Well,

871
00:35:47,820 --> 00:35:49,460
if I don't do anything special,

872
00:35:49,780 --> 00:35:51,300
would that make me look cheap?

873
00:35:51,650 --> 00:35:52,610
No. But I think Gao Zhan

874
00:35:52,860 --> 00:35:54,020
is right about one thing.

875
00:35:54,340 --> 00:35:55,460
You must be sincere.

876
00:35:55,730 --> 00:35:57,420
Jingjing, you can make fun of me.

877
00:35:57,780 --> 00:35:58,300
I

878
00:35:58,530 --> 00:35:59,250
am just short

879
00:35:59,500 --> 00:36:00,730
of digging my heart out
and giving it to her.

880
00:36:05,020 --> 00:36:06,340
Madam Shi

881
00:36:06,570 --> 00:36:07,210
is concerned

882
00:36:07,460 --> 00:36:08,250
that if you get together,

883
00:36:08,610 --> 00:36:09,210
it'll affect

884
00:36:09,460 --> 00:36:10,500
Gao Zhan and Dapeng's studies.

885
00:36:10,730 --> 00:36:11,250
Yes.

886
00:36:11,610 --> 00:36:13,020
So we'll prove to her
that it won't happen

887
00:36:13,250 --> 00:36:14,170
and dispel her doubts!

888
00:36:14,820 --> 00:36:15,210
No...

889
00:36:15,460 --> 00:36:16,650
How... How are you going to prove that?

890
00:36:16,860 --> 00:36:17,610
Be more specific.

891
00:36:17,860 --> 00:36:19,210
Right. Elaborate.

892
00:36:20,940 --> 00:36:21,900
I have an idea.

893
00:36:27,980 --> 00:36:28,610
Um,

894
00:36:29,300 --> 00:36:30,690
Snape didn't make things

895
00:36:31,300 --> 00:36:33,090
difficult for you today, did he?

896
00:36:34,380 --> 00:36:35,090
He didn't try anything today.

897
00:36:36,130 --> 00:36:36,860
That's good.

898
00:36:42,860 --> 00:36:43,860
Um...

899
00:36:44,050 --> 00:36:45,170
How's your room design coming along?

900
00:36:46,940 --> 00:36:48,020
Let me show you my work.

901
00:36:49,460 --> 00:36:49,980
What do you think?

902
00:36:51,780 --> 00:36:52,500
It's okay.

903
00:36:55,020 --> 00:36:55,690
Um...

904
00:36:55,980 --> 00:36:56,780
It looks great!

905
00:36:57,780 --> 00:36:58,420
Forget it.

906
00:36:58,650 --> 00:36:59,650
That's a bit too forced.

907
00:37:00,530 --> 00:37:01,980
But considering your taste,

908
00:37:02,210 --> 00:37:03,210
I guess I shouldn't expect much
from you.

909
00:37:03,530 --> 00:37:04,300
You're right.

910
00:37:04,570 --> 00:37:05,980
I'm not really good with aesthetics.

911
00:37:06,420 --> 00:37:07,690
What do you think of Xu Jingjing, then?

912
00:37:08,820 --> 00:37:09,610
She is okay.

913
00:37:09,940 --> 00:37:10,690
Just okay?

914
00:37:11,020 --> 00:37:11,900
She is the belle of the school!

915
00:37:12,130 --> 00:37:12,900
You're definitely

916
00:37:13,170 --> 00:37:13,940
shortsighted.

917
00:37:14,170 --> 00:37:15,530
You better get that surgery done soon.

918
00:37:15,900 --> 00:37:17,210
But I think you look nice.

919
00:37:17,860 --> 00:37:18,690
You don't just look nice.

920
00:37:19,050 --> 00:37:20,250
You're funny and kind too.

921
00:37:20,460 --> 00:37:20,980
Stop.

922
00:37:25,460 --> 00:37:27,050
Sorry, I'm not good with words.

923
00:37:27,300 --> 00:37:27,900
No, no, no.

924
00:37:28,210 --> 00:37:29,820
That's not what I meant.

925
00:37:32,730 --> 00:37:33,420
Jingjing,

926
00:37:33,730 --> 00:37:34,900
how about

927
00:37:35,980 --> 00:37:36,460
we apply

928
00:37:36,690 --> 00:37:37,420
for universities in Beijing together?

929
00:37:37,900 --> 00:37:38,650
I did my research.

930
00:37:39,020 --> 00:37:39,650
Beijing has a lot

931
00:37:39,900 --> 00:37:40,860
of good art academies too.

932
00:37:49,530 --> 00:37:50,130
(Thank you for your help today.)

933
00:37:50,460 --> 00:37:51,020
(Don't mention it.)

934
00:37:51,250 --> 00:37:51,780
(Xu,)

935
00:37:52,020 --> 00:37:52,980
(we'll be counting on you
for the proposal.)

936
00:37:53,250 --> 00:37:53,980
(What?)

937
00:37:54,210 --> 00:37:54,940
(A proposal?)

938
00:37:55,250 --> 00:37:55,690
(You're going...)

939
00:37:55,940 --> 00:37:56,730
(Gao Zhan. Thank you so much.)
(to be brothers with Gao Zhan for real.)

940
00:37:57,050 --> 00:37:57,820
(Congratulations!)

941
00:37:58,090 --> 00:37:59,530
What?

942
00:38:00,380 --> 00:38:00,940
Why is Gao Zhan

943
00:38:01,170 --> 00:38:02,530
getting Xu Jingjing involved
in his family's affairs?

944
00:38:05,530 --> 00:38:05,980
No.

945
00:38:06,780 --> 00:38:07,570
I can't wait any longer.

946
00:38:16,250 --> 00:38:17,090
Jingjing,

947
00:38:18,250 --> 00:38:19,300
I have to tell you something

948
00:38:19,300 --> 00:38:19,940
that has been

949
00:38:19,980 --> 00:38:20,730
in my heart for a while now.

950
00:38:24,300 --> 00:38:24,940
Xu,

951
00:38:25,170 --> 00:38:25,940
let me tell you something.

952
00:38:26,170 --> 00:38:26,900
Will she beat me up

953
00:38:27,210 --> 00:38:29,380
after she hears what I have to say?

954
00:38:34,980 --> 00:38:35,690
Hey, girl,

955
00:38:35,940 --> 00:38:36,420
do you know

956
00:38:36,650 --> 00:38:37,170
who that online friend

957
00:38:37,460 --> 00:38:38,250
I've been talking to actually is?

958
00:38:43,340 --> 00:38:44,900
It's you.

959
00:38:52,720 --> 00:38:54,520
(Gao Zhan)

960
00:39:00,860 --> 00:39:01,420
Kang Jiawei,

961
00:39:01,820 --> 00:39:02,690
answer me honestly.

962
00:39:03,380 --> 00:39:04,210
Do you think

963
00:39:04,500 --> 00:39:05,650
I'm not normal?

964
00:39:10,570 --> 00:39:11,780
You seem normal to me.

965
00:39:12,250 --> 00:39:13,860
But I don't think I am.

966
00:39:14,570 --> 00:39:15,690
I never know

967
00:39:15,940 --> 00:39:16,300
what to say or do

968
00:39:16,570 --> 00:39:17,530
when I'm around girls.

969
00:39:18,340 --> 00:39:19,500
Are you talking about Xu Jingjing?

970
00:39:21,020 --> 00:39:22,130
Yesterday, I told her

971
00:39:23,170 --> 00:39:23,610
that there are

972
00:39:23,860 --> 00:39:24,780
a lot of good art academies
in Beijing, too,

973
00:39:25,780 --> 00:39:27,020
and she seemed unhappy.

974
00:39:29,420 --> 00:39:30,300
And... After that?

975
00:39:31,250 --> 00:39:32,090
She left.

976
00:39:35,690 --> 00:39:37,210
So this is the emergency

977
00:39:37,460 --> 00:39:39,610
you mentioned over the phone?

978
00:39:41,940 --> 00:39:42,690
Do you know

979
00:39:42,940 --> 00:39:43,300
that I have

980
00:39:43,570 --> 00:39:44,940
something way more important to do?

981
00:39:48,460 --> 00:39:49,130
Sorry.

982
00:39:49,690 --> 00:39:50,340
Am I

983
00:39:50,570 --> 00:39:51,420
taking up your time?

984
00:39:51,860 --> 00:39:52,420
Why don't you go ahead

985
00:39:52,860 --> 00:39:53,980
and do what you need to do?

986
00:39:54,020 --> 00:39:54,780
Forget it.

987
00:39:55,530 --> 00:39:56,380
Since I'm here,

988
00:39:56,900 --> 00:39:58,170
I might as well give you
a few words of advice.

989
00:39:59,650 --> 00:40:00,250
You wanted me

990
00:40:00,530 --> 00:40:01,250
to go over what happened
with you, right?

991
00:40:03,380 --> 00:40:04,530
Yesterday, at the cafe,

992
00:40:04,820 --> 00:40:05,340
Xu Jingjing told you

993
00:40:05,610 --> 00:40:07,020
she was cold, right?

994
00:40:07,500 --> 00:40:08,130
Yes.

995
00:40:08,420 --> 00:40:09,170
What was your reply?

996
00:40:11,250 --> 00:40:13,380
I asked if her feet were cold.

997
00:40:13,860 --> 00:40:14,610
She said yes.

998
00:40:15,300 --> 00:40:16,050
So I said

999
00:40:16,340 --> 00:40:17,420
that it was caused by the sinking

1000
00:40:17,420 --> 00:40:18,300
of the cold air.

1001
00:40:18,690 --> 00:40:21,530
My goodness! My goodness!

1002
00:40:21,860 --> 00:40:22,650
Couldn't you have asked the waiter

1003
00:40:22,900 --> 00:40:24,250
to increase the temperature
of the air conditioner?

1004
00:40:24,530 --> 00:40:25,250
You're right.

1005
00:40:26,090 --> 00:40:27,570
Why didn't I think of that?

1006
00:40:28,610 --> 00:40:29,250
Gao,

1007
00:40:30,380 --> 00:40:31,860
I understand you. I get you.

1008
00:40:32,130 --> 00:40:33,170
But I don't!

1009
00:40:34,050 --> 00:40:34,570
I don't think

1010
00:40:34,860 --> 00:40:35,860
I know anything about girls at all.

1011
00:40:36,900 --> 00:40:38,090
Every time I talk to them,

1012
00:40:38,900 --> 00:40:39,900
I eventually say something wrong.

1013
00:40:40,900 --> 00:40:41,380
But I think

1014
00:40:41,650 --> 00:40:42,610
you know girls quite well.

1015
00:40:42,860 --> 00:40:43,500
I mean,

1016
00:40:44,130 --> 00:40:45,940
what would you have said

1017
00:40:46,170 --> 00:40:46,780
about

1018
00:40:47,130 --> 00:40:47,780
the art teacher?

1019
00:40:48,090 --> 00:40:48,730
In any case,

1020
00:40:48,980 --> 00:40:49,780
I wouldn't say anything nice about him.

1021
00:40:50,130 --> 00:40:50,650
If I did,

1022
00:40:50,940 --> 00:40:51,980
that would mean
going against Xu Jingjing.

1023
00:40:53,170 --> 00:40:54,340
But I think...

1024
00:40:55,020 --> 00:40:56,420
What you think doesn't matter.

1025
00:40:56,690 --> 00:40:57,610
It's what she thinks that matters.

1026
00:40:58,050 --> 00:40:59,020
What are friends for?

1027
00:40:59,380 --> 00:41:00,500
Friends are people
you fawn over people you like with,

1028
00:41:00,730 --> 00:41:01,900
talk bad about others together,

1029
00:41:02,170 --> 00:41:04,050
and an alliance
where you be unreasonable together.

1030
00:41:04,340 --> 00:41:05,020
A united front. Do you understand?

1031
00:41:05,690 --> 00:41:06,300
If it were me,

1032
00:41:06,530 --> 00:41:07,380
I would've complained
about that guy with her.

1033
00:41:07,690 --> 00:41:08,650
I would be even harsher.

1034
00:41:08,940 --> 00:41:09,940
What Snape?

1035
00:41:10,210 --> 00:41:11,130
More like Voldemort.

1036
00:41:11,380 --> 00:41:12,460
Thanos! Megatron!

1037
00:41:14,460 --> 00:41:15,780
Is that all right?

1038
00:41:16,130 --> 00:41:17,780
Of course not.

1039
00:41:19,020 --> 00:41:19,570
But you need

1040
00:41:19,820 --> 00:41:21,940
to let her
get it out of her system first.

1041
00:41:22,210 --> 00:41:24,690
Once she returns to her senses,

1042
00:41:25,020 --> 00:41:25,690
then you can slowly

1043
00:41:25,940 --> 00:41:26,690
tell her

1044
00:41:26,940 --> 00:41:28,500
what you really think.

1045
00:41:28,900 --> 00:41:29,380
If

1046
00:41:29,650 --> 00:41:31,020
she is willing to listen,
then she listens.

1047
00:41:31,210 --> 00:41:31,780
But you need

1048
00:41:32,050 --> 00:41:32,820
to be observant.

1049
00:41:33,340 --> 00:41:34,610
If at any point there are signs

1050
00:41:34,900 --> 00:41:35,780
that you're losing her,

1051
00:41:36,020 --> 00:41:37,420
you turn around
and continue to roast the guy.

1052
00:41:38,860 --> 00:41:39,530
Got it?

1053
00:41:42,340 --> 00:41:43,570
I think I still need
to digest all of that...

1054
00:41:45,820 --> 00:41:46,900
I have to talk bad about him too...

1055
00:41:48,650 --> 00:41:49,610
If she doesn't get it,

1056
00:41:49,730 --> 00:41:50,900
I continue...

1057
00:41:52,610 --> 00:41:53,300
Then...

1058
00:41:53,300 --> 00:41:53,900
Gao,

1059
00:41:54,860 --> 00:41:56,420
you called out to her

1060
00:41:56,690 --> 00:41:57,860
on the rooftop, didn't you?

1061
00:41:58,820 --> 00:41:59,690
What's her take on it?

1062
00:42:00,210 --> 00:42:01,020
She hasn't said

1063
00:42:01,500 --> 00:42:02,300
if she would apply

1064
00:42:02,570 --> 00:42:03,300
to study in Beijing with me.

1065
00:42:03,940 --> 00:42:04,780
But I can wait.

1066
00:42:09,300 --> 00:42:09,980
Gao,

1067
00:42:11,250 --> 00:42:12,500
sometimes,

1068
00:42:12,780 --> 00:42:13,860
you can't force these things.

1069
00:42:14,900 --> 00:42:16,380
Maybe all she wants to do

1070
00:42:16,650 --> 00:42:17,170
right now

1071
00:42:17,460 --> 00:42:18,690
is to concentrate
on preparing for the exam.

1072
00:42:19,380 --> 00:42:20,210
But she's all

1073
00:42:20,500 --> 00:42:22,130
I can think about right now.

1074
00:42:22,500 --> 00:42:23,340
I feel restless

1075
00:42:23,610 --> 00:42:24,500
if I go a day without seeing her.

1076
00:42:25,020 --> 00:42:26,130
Besides, I don't want to be a guy

1077
00:42:26,380 --> 00:42:27,300
who doesn't know
anything about girls anymore.

1078
00:42:27,570 --> 00:42:28,730
I want to be like you.

1079
00:42:29,210 --> 00:42:30,050
Master Kang,

1080
00:42:31,610 --> 00:42:32,650
teach me more of your ways.

1081
00:42:41,170 --> 00:42:42,250
Well, sometimes,
when you learn too many things,

1082
00:42:44,340 --> 00:42:46,380
things can get messy and confusing.

1083
00:42:46,860 --> 00:42:47,730
I'm not worried about that.

1084
00:43:09,730 --> 00:43:10,340
What's the matter?

1085
00:43:11,820 --> 00:43:12,610
Your mood swings

1086
00:43:12,900 --> 00:43:13,860
have been a bit much lately.

1087
00:43:18,340 --> 00:43:18,940
Dad,

1088
00:43:21,570 --> 00:43:23,500
am... am I a coward?

1089
00:43:24,570 --> 00:43:25,900
What's this about?

1090
00:43:27,300 --> 00:43:28,380
It's nothing.

1091
00:43:29,940 --> 00:43:31,300
Oh, don't stop there.

1092
00:43:31,530 --> 00:43:32,210
Tell me.

1093
00:43:36,820 --> 00:43:37,610
Well,

1094
00:43:38,900 --> 00:43:39,780
today,

1095
00:43:39,780 --> 00:43:41,530
someone wanted me to be their teacher

1096
00:43:41,900 --> 00:43:43,420
and help them solve a question.

1097
00:43:45,380 --> 00:43:45,940
And?

1098
00:43:46,900 --> 00:43:48,170
I didn't want to help them,

1099
00:43:49,020 --> 00:43:49,780
but I felt like

1100
00:43:50,050 --> 00:43:51,130
the question was tailor-made for me.

1101
00:43:51,420 --> 00:43:52,170
Only I knew

1102
00:43:52,460 --> 00:43:53,380
the answer to the question.

1103
00:43:56,210 --> 00:43:57,250
So

1104
00:43:59,020 --> 00:44:00,130
I had a chance

1105
00:44:00,420 --> 00:44:01,820
to solve it today.

1106
00:44:02,210 --> 00:44:03,170
But

1107
00:44:03,820 --> 00:44:05,090
I... I couldn't bring myself to do it.

1108
00:44:05,780 --> 00:44:06,690
What's holding you back?

1109
00:44:07,210 --> 00:44:08,130
I... I'm just afraid

1110
00:44:10,170 --> 00:44:11,500
that the answer I have

1111
00:44:11,900 --> 00:44:13,860
isn't the same

1112
00:44:14,130 --> 00:44:15,730
as the one that's given

1113
00:44:16,650 --> 00:44:17,210
on the answer sheet.

1114
00:44:17,300 --> 00:44:19,380
I'm afraid
of misinterpreting the question.

1115
00:44:22,730 --> 00:44:25,650
Well, maybe review the question again?

1116
00:44:26,380 --> 00:44:27,340
Give it some more thought.

1117
00:44:29,300 --> 00:44:30,780
Sometimes,

1118
00:44:31,210 --> 00:44:33,820
it takes time to get an answer.

1119
00:44:34,380 --> 00:44:35,420
Dad, you don't understand.

1120
00:44:36,340 --> 00:44:37,340
I have

1121
00:44:37,780 --> 00:44:38,340
never come across

1122
00:44:38,610 --> 00:44:39,610
such a difficult problem before.

1123
00:44:40,980 --> 00:44:41,900
That's because all those problems

1124
00:44:42,210 --> 00:44:43,500
have never mattered to you.

1125
00:44:47,170 --> 00:44:47,690
Have you

1126
00:44:47,940 --> 00:44:49,090
heard of this saying?

1127
00:44:50,090 --> 00:44:50,900
"Love

1128
00:44:55,050 --> 00:44:56,500
is a touch

1129
00:44:56,780 --> 00:44:58,210
and yet not a touch."

1130
00:44:58,340 --> 00:44:59,130
Dad,

1131
00:45:02,900 --> 00:45:03,820
I'm talking about a question.

1132
00:45:04,170 --> 00:45:05,170
That's what I'm talking about too.

1133
00:45:05,500 --> 00:45:06,420
What does this

1134
00:45:06,690 --> 00:45:07,940
have anything to do with love?

1135
00:45:08,500 --> 00:45:10,250
I thought it was an essay question.

1136
00:45:11,050 --> 00:45:12,730
Where has your mind gone off to?

1137
00:45:17,530 --> 00:45:18,300
Eat.

1138
00:45:18,300 --> 00:45:18,980
Essay?

1139
00:45:20,500 --> 00:45:21,780
I...

1140
00:45:22,050 --> 00:45:22,650
No.

1141
00:45:22,940 --> 00:45:24,050
I was talking about a math problem.

1142
00:45:40,210 --> 00:45:40,730
Tangtang,

1143
00:45:41,650 --> 00:45:42,340
tell Zhou Tian

1144
00:45:42,610 --> 00:45:43,570
to rewrite the first three chapters

1145
00:45:43,900 --> 00:45:44,380
and put more thought into them.

1146
